<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtnfc-ndefrecord.xml">NdefRecord</db:link> type is the base type for all NDEF record types in QML. It contains a single property holding the type of record.</db:para>
<db:para>This class is not intended to be used directly, but extended from C++.</db:para>
